name: Jetta Company Limited
overview:
Jetta Company Limited is a leading Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) in the toys industry. With more than 36 years of solid experience, Jetta has successfully developed sound and proven capabilities in engineering designs, product development, procurement, quality management and manufacturing planning control. Together with its commitment to integrity, excellence and synergy, Jetta today has become one of the most recognized engineering and OEM manufacturing specialists in the industry.

Since its establishment in 1977, Jetta has focused on manufacturing an extended range of toys and gifts products. Today, Jetta has already evolved into one of the largest OEM manufacturers in the world manufacturing both toys and non-toys products. Headquartered in Hong Kong SAR, Jetta currently operates five major production bases in Guangdong Province of China which together cover more than 4.5 million square feet of production floor space and employ a workforce of over 25,000 employees at peak.

At the forefront of this fast-paced industry, Jetta continues to strive for excellence and improvement and aims to be a leader in the development and manufacture of innovative and high quality products. Jetta’s passion, commitment to excellence and all-round professionalism reflect the company’s core values.
